The paper discusses the algorithm selection problem in AI, which involves choosing the most suitable algorithm for solving a given problem instance. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), data structures (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL). However, since the focus is on AI and the paper discusses the state of the art in algorithm selection competitions, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category.
